findings.title: Be careful about using int256
findings.description: The audit report warns about potential issues when using int256 data type.

findings.title: Warning: This contract has a payable fallback function, but no receive ether function
findings.description: The contract has a payable fallback function but lacks a receive ether function, which may lead to unintended behavior.

findings.title: Visibility for constructor is ignored
findings.description: If you want the contract to be non-deployable, making it 'abstract' is sufficient.

findings.title: Do not forget to increase token supply of migrating token
findings.description: The contract does not properly handle increasing the token supply when migrating tokens.

findings.title: Contract don't contain logic to withdraw stuck funds
findings.description: The contract lacks a mechanism to withdraw stuck funds.
